# Input

```scss
.a{
@each $item in$list{
color:$item;
}
}

.b{
@each
$key,$value
in(
  primary: 16px,
secondary:24px
){
font-size:$value;
}
}

.c{
@each $animal in puma,sea-slug,egret,salamander{
color:red;
}
}

```


