# Outputs

## Output 1

-----
Indent style: Tab
Indent width: 2
Line ending: LF
Line width: 80
Quote style: Double Quotes
Trailing newline: true
-----

```scss
.a {
	@each $item in $list {
		color: $item;
	}
}

.b {
	@each $key,
	$value in (
		primary: 16px,
		secondary: 24px,
	) {
		font-size: $value;
	}
}

.c {
	@each $animal in puma, sea-slug, egret, salamander {
		color: red;
	}
}

```
